{"id": 1524, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得你仅有的演技都用在了什么地方？", "description": "人生如戏全靠演技，没有演技强行加戏，你也是一个野生演员吗？（题图来自：Mitch Blunt）", "record_count": 4716, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170220163327k7pZWImVxhoj9MCd.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-02-25T17:00:53Z", "options": [{"id": 172032, "content": "其实和女朋友已经很熟了，但是还是不好意思，于是乎就假装反应迟钝。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208827}, {"id": 180224, "content": "路上碰见了，低头玩手机，假装没看见", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 962224}, {"id": 181760, "content": "上课装作很懂的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977044}, {"id": 172033, "content": "在爸妈面前演戏。小时候，爸妈出门之后在家偷看电视，回来之前先想好剧本。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950354}, {"id": 174337, "content": "我都用在了愚弄我的朋友，亲人，大概是因为相信我，事实可能是我根本没有演技。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957023}, {"id": 172034, "content": "装睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930035}, {"id": 174338, "content": "谈恋爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957029}, {"id": 171523, "content": "每次父母打开房间门，我都在认真地欣赏电脑桌面。", "image": null, "praise_count": 553, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919514}, {"id": 171779, "content": "新买的东西被父母问价的时候\n“不贵不贵，可便宜了”", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701648}, {"id": 177155, "content": "你的作业呢\n忘带了\n你的作业呢\n丢了\n写了吗\n嗯\n那再去抄一遍\n……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957931}, {"id": 178179, "content": "帮忙喊到?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946171}, {"id": 175876, "content": "晚上躲被窝玩手机，父母进门就装睡。学生时代的最强演技", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913404}, {"id": 171525, "content": "打开blued，同事正好看到问这是什么app，我：健身的...诶那个方案怎么说了....?", "image": null, "praise_count": 272, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 128383}, {"id": 171781, "content": "面试的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 934370}, {"id": 171526, "content": "当地铁里/路边的乞讨者/艺人走近自己时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212941}, {"id": 171782, "content": "情侣狗在面前秀恩爱，装作自己真的一点也不尴尬的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933610}, {"id": 172038, "content": "AFK的大部分活动", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192542}, {"id": 172294, "content": "洗澡的时候演技最高:)", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946006}, {"id": 171527, "content": "在前男友面前秀恩爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949220}, {"id": 171783, "content": "老师问：都会了吗……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674121}, {"id": 174855, "content": "上班迟到的原因：钥匙没拿，水管爆了，电表坏了，物业来收钱，出车祸，车坏了，得病了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 754877}, {"id": 171528, "content": "我过的很好，愿你也被温柔对待...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949222}, {"id": 171784, "content": "假装自己是大智若愚，其实是真傻", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 553560}, {"id": 172040, "content": "在家明明躺尸，只要父母在家就会特别忙！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901163}, {"id": 172296, "content": "假装自己不穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 951230}, {"id": 175368, "content": "课堂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 960659}, {"id": 171529, "content": "  假装自己是逗比\n其实根本就是个傻子", "image": null, "praise_count": 157, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931774}, {"id": 171785, "content": "生活……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 947225}, {"id": 172041, "content": "大概是向老师撒谎的时候吧哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948633}, {"id": 172297, "content": "三国杀", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950935}, {"id": 172809, "content": "在公司遇到不喜欢的人还要强颜欢笑的心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 877968}, {"id": 171530, "content": "曾经有多少女朋友？百十来个吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921534}, {"id": 171786, "content": "呵呵笑的很自然", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879955}, {"id": 172042, "content": "上课的时候明明困得不行，强撑着装自己一点都不困 ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940717}, {"id": 182284, "content": "问我妈要钱的时候", "image": "img/option/option/20170322133534gpsifrZywDuzcCP9", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977769}, {"id": 172045, "content": "听别人说笑话。明明不好笑。还要假装哈哈哈。然后强行转移话题。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950014}, {"id": 171790, "content": "在不熟的人面前演技没话说。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949731}, {"id": 172302, "content": "讨厌娇滴滴假惺惺的女生，碍于人情，不得不微笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950910}, {"id": 175375, "content": "上课玩手机假装在听课", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955932}, {"id": 171536, "content": "见到她的时候就像路人一样没有对她特别在意", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680621}, {"id": 171792, "content": "假装不在乎", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949741}, {"id": 171537, "content": "五号玩家预言家 给六号一个金水 强势要警徽～", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 808416}, {"id": 172049, "content": "对父亲撒谎的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942102}, {"id": 171538, "content": "其实需要一个男朋友，相互依存", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949231}, {"id": 171794, "content": "学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933648}, {"id": 172050, "content": "压抑怒气", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911890}, {"id": 173074, "content": "告诉我妈我做完了假期作业然后再最后几天悄悄补", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953951}, {"id": 181522, "content": "过年亲戚打算给你红包的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601806}, {"id": 171539, "content": "哈哈哈~好好笑啊~", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 650722}, {"id": 171795, "content": "看了两边的电影，还要当做第一次看。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949747}]}